data.description: Need space? This beautiful four bedroom, two bathroom, two car garage, home in south Tyler is the answer! This is a brick home has fantastic curb appeal and features carpet, tile and wood plank flooring throughout. The home offers a spacious living room, which highlights a gas burning fireplace and large built-in shelving and cabinets, perfect for movie night! The breakfast area showcases charming French doors, allowing natural light to flood the room. The open kitchen features an quaint dining area and comes equipped with an electric oven/range, dishwasher, built-in microwave and refrigerator. This home also offers the convenience of a laundry room, washer/dryer connections, central heat and air, and a large chain link fenced backyard. Tour this gem today! This property is currently occupied. Please call CPM office at 903/595-0000 to schedule a viewing for this property. No utilities are provided, tenant is responsible for all. If you have a pet or a companion animal you will need to complete a separate screening application for each of them. Application fees are non-refundable. All complete applications will be processed upon receipt. A portion of resident's total monthly amount due will be used to have HVAC filters regularly delivered to their doorstep.
